{"question": "What are some popular IaC tools?", "answer": "Terraform, Ansible, CloudFormation, and Pulumi."},
{"question": "What is the difference between Continuous Delivery and Continuous Deployment?", "answer": "Continuous Delivery keeps code deployable but may deploy manually; Continuous Deployment automatically deploys after tests."},
