{"question": "What is Canary Deployment?", "answer": "Canary Deployment releases a new version to a small subset of users to test before full rollout."},
{"question": "What is Rolling Deployment?", "answer": "Rolling Deployment gradually replaces old version instances with new ones to minimize downtime."},
{"question": "What is DevSecOps?", "answer": "DevSecOps integrates security practices into the DevOps process from the start."},
{"question": "What is Agile methodology?", "answer": "Agile is an iterative software development methodology emphasizing collaboration, customer feedback, and flexibility."},
